                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9210" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1387</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1611 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新型组合债助力“水泥窑”，“绿”动未来 ——海螺创业的绿色环保之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovative Bond Portfolio Powers &#39;Cement Kiln&#39;，  Towards a Green Future --The Green and Environmentally Friendly Path of Conch Venture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潘雪艳，张华，耿玮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国海螺创业有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海螺创业；融资创新；绿色中期票据；绿色发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Conch Venture;Financing Innovation;Green Medium Term Note; Green Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例选择中国海螺创业有限公司（海螺创业）为案例描述对象，梳理了该企业在环保与新能源领域的发展历程。海螺创业自2002年成立以来，通过不断创新和转型，发展成为一家以环保产业为首的多元化企业。为满足大型项目建设的资金需求，海螺创业在2023年发行了两期&quot;绿色+熊猫债+债券通&quot;的创新型中期票据，取得良好市场反响。这不仅拓展了海螺创业的融资渠道，优化了资金结构，同时也彰显了其在环保和新能源领域的领先地位，为推动中部地区乃至全国的绿色发展做出了积极贡献。本案例旨在帮助使用者了解海螺创业如何在环保和新能源领域，通过创新融资方式助力企业实现高质量发展，理解企业在融资过程中面临的风险和应对策略，启发学生思考企业在绿色环保领域中应当承担的责任和使命。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study selects China Conch Venture Holdings Limited (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Conch Venture&quot;) as the subject of analysis, detailing its development trajectory in the environmental protection and renewable energy sectors. Since its establishment in 2002, Conch Venture has evolved into a diversified enterprise with environmental protection as its core business through continuous innovation and transformation. To fulfill the capital requirements for large-scale project construction, Conch Venture issued two innovative medium-term notes in 2023 that incorporated &quot;green bonds, panda bonds, and Bond Connect,&quot; garnering favorable market responses. This not only broadened Conch Venture&#39;s financing channels and optimized its capital structure but also underscored its leadership position in the environmental protection and renewable energy fields, making positive contributions to promoting green development in central China and beyond. The objective of this case study is to assist users in understanding how Conch Venture leverages innovative financing methods to facilitate high-quality development in the environmental protection and renewable energy sectors, grasp the risks faced by the company during the financing process and the corresponding strategies employed, and stimulate students&#39; reflection on the responsibilities and missions that enterprises should undertake in the realm of green environmental protection.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《企业投融资决策》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资方式；中期票据；融资动机；融资风险管理；财务分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
